# Starlight docs (`apps/public-docs`)

Unified **public** user documentation for `docs.newsfork.com` — external API reference, integration guides, legal policies, pricing, FAQ, and company info.

Layout reference: [docs/PLAN-docs-layout-vouus-parity.md](../docs/PLAN-docs-layout-vouus-parity.md) (Vouus-style Layout A splash + Layout B detail).

Content separation plan: [apps/public-docs/docs/PLAN-content-separation.md](../apps/public-docs/docs/PLAN-content-separation.md).

## Layout A vs Layout B

| Layout | Template | Example URLs |
|--------|----------|--------------|
| **A — Main** | `template: splash` + `hero` | `/`, `/ko/` |
| **B — Detail** | default (no `template`) | `/getting-started/`, `/v1/api/seeds-api/` |

- **Layout A:** no sidebar or right TOC; hero + full-width body.
- **Layout B:** 2:5:2 grid (20rem nav + main + 20rem TOC). Use frontmatter `title` for H1 — do not add `#` H1 in markdown body.

## Content paths

- Documentation pages live under `apps/public-docs/src/content/docs/`.
- Korean locale: `apps/public-docs/src/content/docs/ko/`.
- Each sidebar `autogenerate` directory should have an `index.md` or `index.mdx` with frontmatter `title`.

## Public vs internal boundary

**Never publish on public-docs:**

- Wrangler deploy, CI/CD, or `wrangler secret` instructions
- Cloudflare Worker/resource names (`nl-*`, binding keys)
- Internal architecture (queues, R2 raw/prod pipelines, engine internals)
- Admin portal URLs, org account isolation, security runbooks
- Git/Cursor SOP, competitive analysis, internal strategy

Internal engineering guides live in `core-platform/docs/devdocs` (`devdocs.newsfork.com`, Cloudflare Access).

Before adding a page, check `scripts/content-classification.csv` and run `node scripts/audit-public-docs-sensitive.mjs`.

## Sidebar sections

| Directory | Purpose |
| --- | --- |
| Overview (`/`) | Splash home link in sidebar |
| `getting-started.md`, `api-quickstart.md`, `changelog.md` | Start Here |
| `v1/api/` | REST API reference (external developers) |
| `v1/guides/` | Integration guides only — seeds, research, public JSON schemas |
| `legal/` | Privacy, terms, cookies, DPA, SLA |
| `company/` | About, contact, pricing |
| `resources/` | FAQ, glossary |
| `moved/` | Stub pages for retired internal URLs (hidden from sidebar) |

## Deploy

Production deploys to Cloudflare Pages project `nl-public-docs` via `.github/workflows/deploy-public-docs.yml`.

CI runs `scripts/audit-public-docs-sensitive.mjs` before deploy.
